=============================================
HTTP/1.1 201 Created
Content-Length: 0
Date: REGEX(.*)
Location: /ngsi-ld/v1/entities/urn:ngsi-ld:ambient_temperature:335547901



02. Patch it - 200 times
========================
200


03. GET all contexts from the brokers context cache - see only 2
================================================================
